question: I live in the U.A.E.  I am American and I am 34 weeks pregnant.  Protein was found in my urine during my last vist.  My BP was a little high, but has been normal for the past 3 days. I have 6 fibroid tumors and I received my 2nd JJ stent implementation a week ago.  My feet and ankles are swollen,  but no headaches or any other new pains outside of regular pregnancy pains...Braxton Hicks.   What should I expect my doctor's next steps to be? Am I a definite candidate for preeclampsia?
title: Different Country...Different Practices
